A simple "Flappy Bird" style game prototype featuring the Unifor mascot as the playable character. A project that may see improvements in the future.

Basic instructions:
Tap the screen to match the game's pace; the goal is to pass between the towers without colliding.
Failing to jump or jumping too much—causing you to hit the edges—will result in an immediate "game over."

Anyway, I hope you have fun testing my game. It’s a nice way to pass the time :)
